{"content": "I need to multiply 744 \u00d7 807 in base 11.\n\n**Step 1: Convert 744 (base 11) to base 10**\n- 744\u2081\u2081 = 7\u00d711\u00b2 + 4\u00d711\u00b9 + 4\u00d711\u2070\n- = 7\u00d7121 + 4\u00d711 + 4\u00d71\n- = 847 + 44 + 4\n- = 895\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Convert 807 (base 11) to base 10**\n- 807\u2081\u2081 = 8\u00d711\u00b2 + 0\u00d711\u00b9 + 7\u00d711\u2070\n- = 8\u00d7121 + 0 + 7\u00d71\n- = 968 + 0 + 7\n- = 975\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Multiply in base 10**\n- 895 \u00d7 975 = 872,625\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 4: Convert 872,625 back to base 11**\n- 872,625 \u00f7 11 = 79,329 R 6\n- 79,329 \u00f7 11 = 7,211 R 8\n- 7,211 \u00f7 11 = 655 R 6\n- 655 \u00f7 11 = 59 R 6\n- 59 \u00f7 11 = 5 R 4\n- 5 \u00f7 11 = 0 R 5\n\nReading remainders from bottom to top: 546668\n\n**Answer: 546668**", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 363, "completion_tokens": 394}